ont sensing using both PW and SCC. The speckle\nintensity in the coronagraphic image was then minimized using PW+EFC and SCC\nindependently. We demonstrate that both SCC and PW+EFC can generate a dark hole\nin space-like conditions in a few iterations. Both techniques reach the current\nlimitation of our laboratory bench and provide coronagraphic contrast levels of\n5e-9 in a narrow spectral band (<0.25% bandwidth)\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 9 Mar 2020 18:12:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-04-08"}
